snippet.title: Guy thinks I can't play Rush E and calls me a liar
snippet.description:
why not, challenge accepted

"Because it was mediocre, no offense." Merch: https://www.themeeksduo.com/merchandise/fanchen-collection

Read description for plot update!
First, go show some love to https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utYanxGgTww
Don't spread hate.
Unfortunately the legendary comment thread has been deleted due to the closing of Prolitening's previous school account. Nevertheless, please go support his new channel!


I also thank the lord Jesus Charlie himself for blessing this video https://youtu.be/foSAi-olfck

For those who are wondering, the plot had achieved a *good ending* status. Try to find Hen\*ai guy’s comment in Cr1tikal’s video. We’re basically married now.

My idea of mediocrity is that it had room for improvement, it was not bad. Wasn’t trying to insult the performance, just an honest opinion. Obviously could have worded that better though! Prolitening told me he understood my intentions were not hostile, so we pals now. Stay tuned for potential collab!

Edit 2: The potential collab is happening! Come check out the Ultimate Rush E for 8 hands! Featuring @litening5826, @TheMeeksDuo, and myself!
